+     * (0,ASCII) B256(A) (3) --> (1,B256)
+     * (0,ASCII) EDF(AB) (4) --> (2,EDF)
+     * (0,ASCII) C40(ABC) (3) --> (3,C40)
+     * (0,ASCII) TEXT(ABC) (5) --> (3,TEXT)
